comments: After the pick, Washington (CHA) and Allen (BKN) engage and disengage as Washington immediately slides his hand off Allen's waist without affecting his FOM.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) lifts his pivot foot on the perimeter.
Durant (BKN) and Biyombo (CHA) engage and disengage off-ball as Biyombo begins his dive toward the basket.
Irving (BKN) has a resting forearm on Washington's (CHA) back in the post as Washington jumps towards the perimeter to receive the pass.
Washington (CHA) dislodges Irving (BKN) from his legal guarding position in the post.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Allen (BKN) turns his shoulder and delivers contact to Washington (CHA) during the screen.
During the screen, Irving (BKN) immediately slides his hand off Rozier's (CHA) waist without affecting his FOM.
During the drive, Irving (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position on Hayward (CHA) and makes clean ball contact on his steal attempt.
Irving (BKN) maintains his legally obtained position as incidental contact with Biyombo (CHA) occurs after he jumps to grab the rebound.
The ball never touches the rim on the shot by Washington (CHA) and the 24 second shot clock expires.
Durant (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Rozier's (CHA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Washington (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in Luwawu-Cabarrot's path (BKN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Allen (BKN) is retreating and marginal contact occurs when he brushes Washington's (CHA) off-arm on his driving shot attempt.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) jumps from point A to point B, making contact with Washington's (CHA) back and head that affects his ability to follow through naturally on his play at the basket.
Washington (CHA) briefly places his hand on Durant's (BKN) waist and immediately slides it off as Durant begins to move away.
Durant (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Rozier's (CHA) path and incidental foot to foot contact occurs.
During the rebound, Graham (CHA) engages with Allen (BKN) and his legal hand gets tangled with Allen's jersey. The contact is incidental and does not affect Allen's FOM.

During the rebound, Washington (CHA) and Allen (BKN) mutually engage as their arms come together and separate.  As the two players disengage, Washington loses his balance and his momentum takes him to the floor.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Hayward (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position on Irving (BKN) as Irving slips and falls to the floor as he starts his dribble.
Martin (CHA) and Biyombo (CHA) dive for the loose ball and any contact with Harris (BKN) is deemed incidental. Harris does not touch the ball until he establishes himself back in bounds.
